## 🧠 About Me

A geophysicist specializing in seismic interpretation, geophysical data analysis, and numerical modeling, with a strong research focus on fault mechanics and earthquake dynamics. Skilled in high-velocity friction experiments and proficient in tools such as Petrel, Geolog, Python, and MATLAB for seismic data processing and analysis.

